See [ci.yml](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/.github/workflows/ci.yml).

## Project Structure

- [src/main.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/main.rs): CLI entrypoint and command dispatch
- [src/config.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/config.rs): config loading and validation
- [src/db.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/db.rs): migrations and repository operations
- [src/chunker.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/chunker.rs): markdown-aware chunking
- [src/ingest.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/ingest.rs): embed pipeline
- [src/search.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/search.rs): BM25/vector/hybrid retrieval
- [src/api.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/api.rs): OpenAI-compatible API calls
- [src/mcp.rs](/Users/origo/src/iqmd-rs/src/mcp.rs): MCP stdio/HTTP server surfaces

